    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约在学校施加对智能手机的禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/new-york-state-to-impose-whole-day-ban-on-cellphones-in-schools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据旨在改善儿童心理健康的新预算协议，纽约州立法领导人已同意禁止在公立学校使用智能手机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/new-york-state-to-impose-whole-day-ban-on-cellphones-in-schools</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 23:16:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着威胁的增长，加拿大贸易平衡转向赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/canada-s-trade-balance-flips-to-deficit-as-tariff-threats-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着特朗普政府关税的威胁和实施开始重新汇款全球交易流动，加拿大向其最大客户，美国以及其他国家的出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/canada-s-trade-balance-flips-to-deficit-as-tariff-threats-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 12:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
